[
    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442440",
        "quote": "I say: If you don't know how to cook, I'm sure you have at least one friend who knows how to cook. Well, call that friend and say, 'Can I come next time and can I bring some food and can I come an hour or two hours ahead and watch you and help you?'",
