    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442442",
        "quote": "I am a glutton. I'll eat whatever is there. Pizza. I love hot dogs anywhere. I've got nothing against any of that. If I feel like eating, I eat. I don't feel guilty about it at all.",
