    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442447",
        "quote": "I taped my first series for PBS in 1982 at WJCT-TV in Jacksonville, Florida. The show, called 'Everyday Cooking with Jacques Pepin,' was about saving time and money in the kitchen - and it was a celebration of simple and unpretentious food.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jacques Pepin",
