    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442434",
        "quote": "After 45 years of marriage, when I have an argument with my wife, if we don't agree, we do what she wants. But, when we agree, we do what I want!",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jacques Pepin",
            "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442434"
