    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442429",
        "quote": "The idea of old was to conform yourself to a style of cooking, it was not to create a style of cooking. Now the chef is so much into 'I want to sign that dish and say I am the one who made that dish.'",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jacques Pepin",
            "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442429"
        },
