    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442439",
        "quote": "You can't escape the taste of the food you had as a child. In times of stress, what do you dream about? Your mother's clam chowder. It's security, comfort. It brings you home.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jacques Pepin",
            "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442439"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Stress",
