            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442424",
        "quote": "This is what a family is all about - one another, sitting around the table at night. And it's very, very important, I think, for the kid to spend time not only around the table eating with their parents, but in the kitchen.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jacques Pepin",
            "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442424"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Think",
