    {
        "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442449",
        "quote": "Just because I am a chef doesn't mean I don't rely on fast recipes. Indeed, we all have moments when, pressed for time, we'll use a can of tuna and a tomato for a first course. It's a question of choosing the right recipes for the rest of the menu.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jacques Pepin",
            "url": "/quotes/jacques_pepin_442449"
        },
